data.title: Princess Astrid of Sweden & Leopold of Belgium Engagement
data.meta_description: Prints of The official engagement photograph (taken on 21st September 1926) of Princess Astrid of Sweden
data.text:
The official engagement photograph (taken on 21st September 1926) of Princess Astrid of Sweden, born Astrid Sofia Lovisa Thyra ) and the future King Leopold III of Belgium. Astrid was killed tragically in a car crash. Date: 1926. Mary Evans Picture Library makes available wonderful images created for people to enjoy over the centuries.
